---
import site from '@/lib/site';
---

<section class="section section--tint hfk-s3-process">
  <div class="container">

    <div class="hfk-s3__intro">
      <h2 class="hfk-s3__heading">Your Rejuvenating Hydrafacial Keravive Experience</h2>

      <p class="hfk-s3__body">
        HydraFacial™ Keravive™ is the first-of-its-kind scalp health treatment that cleanses, stimulates, nourishes, and hydrates the scalp using HydraFacial™ technology. The treatment targets the scalp and hair follicles, removing follicle-clogging debris and delivering a powerful blend of growth factors and skin proteins directly to the scalp.
      </p>

      <p class="hfk-s3__body">
        The treatment is completed with a take-home spray to extend the benefits and help you maintain healthier-looking hair between appointments. Most clients see noticeable improvements in scalp health and hair appearance after just a few sessions.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="hfk-s3__steps">

      <div class="hfk-s3__step">
        <h3 class="hfk-s3__step-title">CLEANSE + EXFOLIATE</h3>
        <p class="hfk-s3__step-body">
          HydraFacial™ Vortex Technology deeply cleanses and exfoliates the scalp, removing follicle-clogging sebum, dirt, and environmental debris.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="hfk-s3__step">
        <h3 class="hfk-s3__step-title">HYDRATE + NOURISH</h3>
        <p class="hfk-s3__step-body">
          A proprietary blend of growth factors, skin proteins, and hyaluronic acid is infused into the scalp to nourish and hydrate hair follicles for a healthier environment.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="hfk-s3__step">
        <h3 class="hfk-s3__step-title">EXTEND + ENHANCE</h3>
        <p class="hfk-s3__step-body">
          A take-home HydraFacial™ Keravive™ Peptide Complex Spray is provided to extend the benefits of the in-office treatment and support ongoing scalp health.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>

    <div class="hfk-s3__cta">
      <a
        href={site.calcomUrl}
        class="btn btn--primary btn--lg"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
      >
        Schedule Now
      </a>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .hfk-s3__intro {
    max-width: var(--container-narrow);
    margin-inline: auto;
    text-align: center;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-sm);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .hfk-s3__heading {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-h2);
    font-weight: var(--weight-regular);
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  .hfk-s3__body {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .hfk-s3__steps {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-lg);
    width: 100%;
  }

  .hfk-s3__step {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-xs);
    padding: var(--space-md);
    background: var(--color-bg);
    border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgb(0 0 0 / 0.05);
  }

  .hfk-s3__step-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    font-weight: var(--weight-semibold);
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  .hfk-s3__step-body {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .hfk-s3__cta {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-top: var(--space-lg);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .hfk-s3__steps {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .hfk-s3__cta .btn {
      width: 100%;
      text-align: center;
    }
  }
</style>
